#### Conditional Classes

Use utility functions for conditional classes:

```typescriptreact
import { cn } from "@/lib/utils";

<div
  className={cn(
    "base-class",
    isActive && "active-class",
    variant === "primary" ? "primary-class" : "secondary-class"
